Interface ProvisionerOOB

      • minLengthOfOOBData

        int minLengthOfOOBData()
        Returns:
        Value that specifies minimum allowed input/output OOB data length. A value of 0 is interpreted as default value of 1 when setting OOB authentication requirements.

      • maxLengthOfOOBData

        int maxLengthOfOOBData()
        Returns:
        Value that specifies maximum allowed input/output OOB data length. A value of 0 is interpreted as default value of 8 when setting OOB authentication requirements.
